{"tid":2306360,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[美國大選] 今次美國大選舞弊到咁撚核突，其實美國人自係點睇？","createTime":"2020-11-30T11:22:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-30T14:38:24.000Z","uid":52658,"like":26,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"9a8426e08874930edbe8b4a764a9e4548e918e7a","tid":2306360,"uid":52658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:22:52.000Z","msg":"美國人係咪真係完全無感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n有無人分享下<br />\n<br />\n我自己有兩個親戚係美國人黎<br />\n一個係夏威夷州教緊書<br />\n佢老公係加州做緊I banker <br />\n呢兩條友真係晒鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同佢講過下佢地既選舉<br />\n佢地死都覺得美國唔存在舞弊問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n到我比晒d證據佢睇<br />\n包括拜登既票點到好唔尋常<br />\n川普既票比人撕爛晒 賓州點票員係度自己劃選票等等<br />\n佢地只係識係度跳針話自己相信美國既司法制度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然佢無講出口<br />\n但我感覺佢係只要可以踢走Donald Trump <br />\n佢就唔會介意d乜野選舉舞弊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n都九唔撚搭八<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />廢鳩事理佢而家都<br />\n<br />\n另一個就係田納西州做農場主<br />\n呢個就比較同聲同氣d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />日日係度屌柒民主黨做假票<br />\n<br />\n美國人好多都好無知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實美國係有好多不問世事乜都唔知既美豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4e986b14949be7265210a6c7f3d95716451720e","tid":2306360,"uid":370061,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-30T11:26:22.000Z","msg":"扮訓既人係叫唔醒嘅"},{"pid":"02a28db42073f46d5132a7557d939a625cb4608c","tid":2306360,"uid":